org.apache.juneau.rest.response

Class MovedPermanently

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.rest.response.HttpResponse
      • org.apache.juneau.rest.response.MovedPermanently

  • @Response(code=301,
          description="Moved Permanently")
 @BeanIgnore
public class MovedPermanently
extends HttpResponse
    Represents an HTTP 301 Moved Permanently response.

    This and all future requests should be directed to the given URI.
